{"metadata":{"externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNMapSnapshotter(im)addAnnotations:","symbolKind":"method","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"roleHeading":"Instance Method","title":"addAnnotations:","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"- "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"addAnnotations:"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"addAnnotations:"}]},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Adds an array of annotations to the snapshotter."}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapsnapshotter\/addannotations:"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshotter"]]},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"text":"- (","kind":"text"},{"text":"void","preciseIdentifier":"c:v","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"addAnnotations:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"NSArray<id<MLNAnnotation>>","preciseIdentifier":"c:Q$objc(cs)NSArray","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" *) ","kind":"text"},{"text":"annotations","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"platforms":["iOS"]}]},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"name":"annotations","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"An array of annotation objects. Each object in the array"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"must conform to the "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" protocol. The snapshotter retains each"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"individual annotation object."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion","type":"heading"},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":""},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPolyline"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPolyline"},{"type":"text","text":", and "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPolyline"},{"type":"text","text":" objects"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"cannot be added to the snapshotter at this time. Nor can "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPoint"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"objects that are not instances of "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPolyline"},{"type":"text","text":" or "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPolyline"},{"type":"text","text":". Any"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"multipoint, multipolyline, multipolygon, or shape collection objects that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"are specified are silently ignored."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"style":"note","name":"Note","type":"aside"}]}],"sections":[],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshotter\/addAnnotations:","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotation":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" protocol is used to provide annotation-related information"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to a map view. To use this protocol, you adopt it in any custom objects that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"store or represent annotation data. Each object then serves as the source of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"information about a single map annotation and provides critical information,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"such as the annotation’s location on the map. Annotation objects do not provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the visual representation of the annotation but typically coordinate (in"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"conjunction with the map view’s delegate) the creation of an appropriate"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"objects to handle the display."}],"role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"MLNAnnotation","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"MLNAnnotation","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"title":"MapLibre","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","type":"topic","role":"collection","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling."}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapSnapshotter/addAnnotations:":{"fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"- "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"addAnnotations:"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"addAnnotations:"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshotter\/addAnnotations:","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapsnapshotter\/addannotations:","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","title":"addAnnotations:","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Adds an array of annotations to the snapshotter."}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMultiPolyline":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":