role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNMapSnapshotOptions"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapsnapshotoptions","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshotOptions"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNPolyline":{"title":"MLNPolyline","role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnpolyline","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPolyline","type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" object represents a shape consisting of two or more vertices,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"specified as "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"CLLocationCoordinate2D"},{"type":"text","text":" instances, and the line segments that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"connect them. For example, you could use an polyline to represent a road or the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"path along which something moves."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPolyline","fragments":[{"text":"MLNPolyline","kind":"identifier"}],"kind":"symbol","type":"topic"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapSnapshotterDelegate":{"abstract":[{"text":"Optional methods about significant events when creating a snapshot using an","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshotter","isActive":true},{"text":" object.","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNMapSnapshotterDelegate"}],"title":"MLNMapSnapshotterDelegate","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshotterDelegate","role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapsnapshotterdelegate","type":"topic"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapSnapshotter":{"fragments":